<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='159:185'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-1a' );" name="041-1a" class="pb">[041-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='185:194'>　周易略例考證</span>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='194:220'>　<span class='krp-note'>臣良裘/</span>按略例一册乃王氏易註之綱領隋書經籍</span>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='220:243'>　志所謂周易十卷蓋併此數之故釋文云或有題爲</span>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='243:266'>　第十者孔氏作疏主申王學而不疏略例殊失體要</span>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='266:289'>　至坊刻注疏本乃削去之謬妄甚矣監本雖附見卷</span>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='289:312'>　末而序目不全字句多譌今據相臺岳氏所梓荆谿</span>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='312:335'>　家塾本及漢魏叢書津逮秘書所錄稍爲叅訂有同</span>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='335:342'>　異者著之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='342:368'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-1b' );" name="041-1b" class="pb">[041-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='368:372'>明彖</span>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='372:395'>明其所由之主也注明辯也辯卦體功用所由之主○</span>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='395:413'>　監本脫明辯也三字依漢魏叢書本添</span>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='413:436'>貞夫一者也注制其動者貞正之一者也○荆谿家塾</span>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='436:443'>　本無正字</span>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='443:466'>主必致一也注故无心于存皆得其存也○監本脫此</span>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='466:478'>　二句依津逮秘書本添</span>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='478:501'>則知可以執一御也注无爲之一者道也君也○監本</span>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='501:527'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-2a' );" name="041-2a" class="pb">[041-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='527:539'>　脫此九字依荆谿本添</span>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='539:562'>或有遺爻而舉二體者卦體不由乎爻也注棄此一爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='562:585'>　而舉二體以明其義○棄此一爻秘書本作棄此中</span>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='585:591'>　之一爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='591:611'>其孰能與於此乎○監本脫乎字依叢書本添</span>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='611:617'>明爻通變</span>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='617:640'>故合散屈伸與體相乖注人之多辟已獨處正○處荆</span>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='640:647'>　谿本作取</span>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='647:673'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-2b' );" name="041-2b" class="pb">[041-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='673:696'>召雲者龍命呂者律注召水氣者水畜此明有識感无</span>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='696:719'>　識命陰呂者陽律此明无識感有識○无識感有識</span>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='719:735'>　句諸本皆同監本作无識感无識</span>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='735:758'>異而知其通注男女睽而其志同也○同秘書本作通</span>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='758:768'>　睽彖𫝊本作通</span>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='768:788'>語成而後有格○叢書本作語成器而後有格</span>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='788:811'>鼔舞而天下從者見乎其情者也○監本從字下脫者</span>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='811:820'>　字依叢書本添</span>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='820:846'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-3a' );" name="041-3a" class="pb">[041-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='846:869'>一陰一陽而无窮注道者虚无也○監本脫无字依荆</span>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='869:875'>　谿本添</span>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='875:883'>明卦適變通爻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='883:906'>故卦以反對而爻亦有變注爻變亦準也○準監本作</span>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='906:915'>　應依荆谿本改</span>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='915:938'>唯變所適注卦旣推移故道用无常○旣監本作雖道</span>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='938:951'>　字上脫故字依秘書本添</span>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='951:974'>險易之象也注需卦九三近坎險也○坎監本作難依</span>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='974:1000'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-3b' );" name="041-3b" class="pb">[041-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1000:1007'>　荆谿本改</span>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1007:1030'>物競而獨安於靜者要其終也○監本脫於字依秘書</span>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1030:1035'>　本添</span>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1035:1058'>辯逆順者存乎承乘注陰乘乎陽逆也○諸本多作陽</span>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1058:1071'>　乘乎陰誤也今依荆谿本</span>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1071:1075'>明象</span>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1075:1098'>言生於象故可尋言以觀象象生於意故可尋象以觀</span>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1098:1117'>　意○兩生字監本並作主字依秘書本改</span>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1117:1143'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-4a' );" name="041-4a" class="pb">[041-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1143:1166'>得意而忘象注旣得乾意其龍可捨○注意字監本譌</span>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1166:1176'>　作象依秘書本改</span>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1176:1199'>存言者非得象者也注未得象者存言言則非象○則</span>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1199:1220'>　監本譌作有下象則非意句同俱依荆谿本改</span>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1220:1224'>辯位</span>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1224:1247'>乾上九貴而無位注陽居之也需上六雖不當位注隂</span>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1247:1270'>　居之也○監本陽譌作隂隂譌作陽俱依荆谿本改</span>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1270:1293'>應貴賤之序者也注各守其位應之以序○序監本作</span>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1293:1319'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-4b' );" name="041-4b" class="pb">[041-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1319:1328'>　事依叢書本改</span>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1328:1333'>畧例下</span>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1333:1356'>其有先貞後亨者亨由于貞也○監本脫下亨字依秘</span>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1356:1362'>　書本添</span>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1362:1366'>卦畧</span>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1366:1385'>洽乃疑亡也○洽監本譌作始依叢書本改</span>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1385:1388'>　</span>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1388:1397'>　周易略例考證</span>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1397:1423'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-5a' );" name="041-5a" class="pb">[041-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1423:1449'>　　少詹事<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>朱良裘謹言按孔頴達易疏序云爲之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1449:1472'>　　正義十有四卷經籍考館閣書目云今本止十三</span>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1472:1495'>　　卷監本分爲九卷蓋據王弼注六十四卦六卷韓</span>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1495:1518'>　　伯注繫辭以下三卷之文而又不依其篇第也諸</span>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1518:1541'>　　經題曰注疏而易獨名爲兼義諸經分録音義而</span>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1541:1564'>　　易獨附之卷末直是合刻注疏之始體例未定故</span>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1564:1584'>　　爾乖違後人遂沿而不改耳乾隆四年奉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1584:1607'>敕校刋經史廣羅舊本以備叅稽得文淵閣所藏不全</span>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1607:1633'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-5b' );" name="041-5b" class="pb">[041-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1633:1656'>　　易疏四冊則上經三十卦釐爲五卷始知孔疏王</span>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1656:1679'>　　注已分六卷爲十卷合之韓注三卷而十三卷自</span>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1679:1708'>　　備<span class='krp-note'>臣良裘/</span>偕<span class='krp-note'>臣林枝春臣聞棠臣吳泰/</span>昕夕考究</span>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1708:1731'>　　凡監本舛錯謬訛之處證以舊本如覆得發如垢</span>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1731:1754'>　　得梳惜自晉卦以下舊本殘缺然監本之不可復</span>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1754:1775'>　　讀者已十去其六七矣是年冬校訖進呈奉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1775:1804'>制報可爰付剞劂逾年竣工兹<span class='krp-note'>臣良裘/</span>復與同事<span class='krp-note'>臣陳/</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1804:1830'>　　<span class='krp-note'>浩臣李清植/</span>覆加檢覈詳審再三錄爲周易注疏</span>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1830:1856'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-6a' );" name="041-6a" class="pb">[041-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1856:1866'>　　考證若干條遵</span>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1866:1889'>㫖列於各卷之末竊惟王弼易注孤行江左二百餘年</span>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1889:1913'>　　孔氏正義專申其學㡬扵盡掃羣言自程朱𫝊義</span>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1913:1936'>　　出學者乃束而不觀今其說之合者已備錄於周</span>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1936:1960'>　　易折中無容更爲論别漢世𫝊易諸家異同不可</span>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1960:1983'>　　復考間有見於李鼎祚集解者採輯一二以補陸</span>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1983:2007'>　　德明釋文所未備王注流𫝊差謬郭京所舉正者</span>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2007:2030'>　　總一百三節世罕其書今分别著之其疏釋中字</span>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2030:2056'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0007', 'WYG', '041-6b' );" name="041-6b" class="pb">[041-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2056:2079'>　　有訛别各加指證以資考索他如五經文字六經</span>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2079:2102'>　　正誤音辯韻補諸書所訂正足爲字學韻學之助</span>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2102:2125'>　　者亦采其說以附於識小之義深知測海之難實</span>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2125:2142'>　　切負山之懼<span class='krp-note'>臣良裘/</span>謹識</span>
</p>
